    • set_is_add

      public void set_is_add(boolean is_add)
      Sets the form to add a new part or modify an existing one. To avoid having to create two separate forms, this method is used to set the form to either add a new part or modify an existing one.
      Parameters:
      is_add - True if adding a new part, false if modifying an existing one. FUTURE ENHANCEMENT: This method could be replaced by a check if part is null.
